diagram:
flowchart TD
  Start[Workload] --> Existing{Existing OS or vendor dependency?}
  Existing -- yes --> VM[VMs or VM Scale Sets]
  Existing -- no --> Web{HTTP web app or API?}
  Web -- yes --> AppSvc[App Service]
  Web -- containerized and bursty --> ACA[Container Apps]
  Web -- no --> Event{Event driven small code?}
  Event -- yes --> Func[Functions]
  Event -- no --> Orchestrate{Need Kubernetes API or custom orchestration?}
  Orchestrate -- yes --> AKS[AKS]
  Orchestrate -- no --> Parallel{Large parallel batch job?}
  Parallel -- yes --> Batch[Azure Batch]
  Parallel -- no --> Recheck[Recheck constraints cost and ops model]
